---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { ChevronLeft, ShieldCheck } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Neurolytix AI Solutions" noindex={true}>
  <div
    class="relative min-h-screen bg-[#0F172A] text-[#F8FAFC] py-16 px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 selection:bg-[#38BDF8]/30 overflow-hidden font-jakarta"
  >
    {/* Decorative background glow */}
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-4xl h-96 bg-[#38BDF8]/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none -z-10"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      {/* Navigation */}
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#38BDF8] hover:text-[#818CF8] transition-colors group font-inter font-medium"
        >
          <ChevronLeft
            className="w-5 h-5 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(56,189,248,0.5)]"
          />
          <span>Back to Home</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* Header */}
      <div class="mb-12 border-b border-white/10 pb-8 relative">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div
            class="p-3 bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden group"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#38BDF8]/20 to-[#818CF8]/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
            >
            </div>
            <ShieldCheck
              className="w-8 h-8 text-[#38BDF8] drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(56,189,248,0.5)] relative z-10"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1
              class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-inter font-bold text-white tracking-tight drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(56,189,248,0.3)]"
            >
              Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p
              class="text-[#38BDF8] font-inter font-medium mt-2 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#38BDF8] animate-pulse"
              ></span>
              Verified Secure & Privacy First
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Content */}
      <div
        class="bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl relative z-10"
      >
        <div
          class="prose prose-invert prose-cyan max-w-none font-jakarta [&>h2]:font-inter [&>h2]:font-bold [&>h3]:font-inter [&>h3]:font-semibold prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-li:leading-relaxed prose-p:text-gray-300 prose-li:text-gray-300"
        >
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            At Neurolytix AI Solutions, we respect your privacy and are
            committed to protecting it through our compliance with this policy.
            This Privacy Policy outlines the types of data we collect, including
            Personal and Project-related information, and how we utilize,
            safeguard, and disclose that data.
          </p>

          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Contact Details:</strong> Name, Email address, Phone number,
              and related contact details.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Project Information:</strong> Requirements, technical documentation,
              specifications, and data necessary for the execution of our services.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Log Data:</strong> IP addresses, browser type, operating system,
              and standard web analytics collected automatically as you navigate through
              our site.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We use information that we collect about you or that you provide to
            us to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide our services and customized software solutions.</li>
            <li>Process payments and securely manage your transactions.</li>
            <li>
              Communicate project updates, respond to your comments, questions,
              and requests.
            </li>
            <li>
              Improve and refine our AI algorithms and software architectures
              based on usage patterns.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2>AI Data Handling</h2>
          <p>
            Client data utilized for custom AI model integration and processing
            is kept strictly confidential. <strong
              >We do not use your proprietary or client-specific data to train
              public or third-party AI models without explicit consent.</strong
            > Your intellectual property remains yours, and our handling of data adheres
            to strict confidentiality agreements.
          </p>

          <h2>Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement industry-standard encryption protocols and secure
            hosting practices to maintain the safety of your personal and
            project information. Our infrastructure utilizes secure third-party
            providers such as AWS, Vercel, and Netlify to ensure high
            availability, end-to-end encryption, and a robust security posture
            against unauthorized access.
          </p>

          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track the
            activity on our service and hold certain information. Cookies are
            files with small amounts of data which may include an anonymous
            unique identifier. You can instruct your browser to refuse all
            cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent to enhance your
            user experience according to your preferences.
          </p>

          <h2>Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            <strong
              >We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personally
              identifiable information to outside parties.</strong
            > This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in operating
            our website, conducting our business, or servicing you, so long as those
            parties agree to keep this information confidential.
          </p>

          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            Depending on your location, you may have the following rights
            regarding your personal data:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              The right to access, update, or delete the personal information we
              have on you.
            </li>
            <li>
              The right of rectification to have your information corrected if
              it is inaccurate or incomplete.
            </li>
            <li>
              The right to withdraw consent at any time where we relied on your
              explicit consent to process your personal information.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the practices
            of this site, or your dealings with our services, please contact us
            at:
            <br />
            <a
              href="mailto:rishabhraghwendra2002@gmail.com"
              class="text-[#38BDF8] hover:text-[#818CF8] transition-colors inline-block mt-2 font-medium"
              >rishabhraghwendra2002@gmail.com</a
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
